The '''Kenobi Medallion''' was a bronze medal that was awarded to [[Alliance Army/Legends|Alliance Army]] personnel for displaying extraordinary acts of bravery in combat. It was a sixth embellishment to the [[Kalidor Crescent/Legends|Kalidor Crescent]] enacted shortly after the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], initially as a means to posthumously honor those who fell in combat during said battle.

The medal, named for the famous [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]], was supplied posthumously to [[Jek Tono Porkins/Legends|Jek Tono Porkins]] for his role in the Battle of Yavin.<ref name="GG1">''[[Galaxy Guide 1: A New Hope]]''</ref> It was later given to [[Reyé Hollis/Legends|Reyé Hollis]] for his service during the [[Battle of Hoth/Legends|Battle of Hoth]].<ref name="CCG">{{CCG|set=Special Edition Limited|cardname=Sergeant Hollis}}</ref>

